{"tid":1975342,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"滑翔機Sailplane - 男人老狗揸個廢牌","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T03:14:21.000Z","uid":65222,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2582b3be7c576b4753aef3a0b2ee1636e6c3b726","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/b4YrpmhgNGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fb4YrpmhgNGs&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=6bcf56c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/embed/b4YrpmhgNGs</a><br />\n<br />\n最近因為武漢肺炎被迫放假突然多左好多時間，心血來潮想寫個post分享下滑翔機呢樣野。<br />\n<br />\n少少背景:<br />\n幾年前係英國返左一年同飛機有關既intern，屎忽痕走左去搵啲野weekend玩下，上網見到原來附近有個滑翔機Club，啲introductory flight都唔貴咁就走左去左試下。點知試完之後就上撚左癮，最後就用個一年時間去學飛Glider。<br />\n咩係滑翔機？<br />\nWiki:<br />\n//滑翔機（英文：Glider）是指不依靠動力裝置飛行的重於空氣的固定翼航空器，起飛後僅依靠空氣作用於其升力面上的反作用力進行自由飛行。//<br />\n滑翔機英文又可以叫Glider或者Sailplane，最早係19世紀已經出現，簡單黎講其實就係一部冇引擎既飛機（男人老狗揸個廢牌），係有動力飛機之前主要用黎研究飛行原理同飛機設計等等。莱特兄弟係整Flyer I之前都用左大量時間係滑翔機上面實驗佢地既設計。但因為當時滑翔機既性能限制，一直都冇咩實際既用途，一戰之後滑翔機就主要循軍事方向發展，去到二戰，開始有載重量達20噸既大型運輸滑翔機出現（呢到唔詳細講，我都唔係太清楚）。<br />\n<br />\nLuftwaffe Messerschmitt Me 321 Cargo Glider<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0zQ06y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0zQ06y.jpg&h=e40b59f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n去到近呢幾十年，滑翔機主要都係用係通用飛行(General Aviation)，姐係d人娛樂性質間唔時得閒去飛下，世界各地的每年都會有好多唔同既比賽俾唔同程度既滑翔機機師參加。以英國為例，每年都會有一場全國比賽舉行(UK National Gliding Championships)。而同F1一樣， 滑翔機都有自己既Grand Prix，比賽方式有幾種，最普遍係鬥快完成一條由幾個點組成既空中賽道。我自己覺得睇Gliding Grand Prix見到啲滑翔機同個懸崖貼住飛仲刺激過睇F1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n滑翔機本身冇動力，所以要靠合適既天氣情況延長滯空時間，用3幅圖講下：<br />\n1. Thermal<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmfgWG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmfgWG0.jpg&h=9d7d0a6f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. Ridge Lift<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1v1onH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1v1onH.jpg&h=dbaf85f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. Wave<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PtxCF9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPtxCF9F.jpg&h=9bd02bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為唔使燃料，天氣好個陣可以飛幾百公里玩成日，你最大既敵人係你個膀胱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多topic好難一次過講晒，如果有某一part想知都可以問，除左唔識都會儘量答。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmeEUw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmeEUw3.jpg&h=08d7a307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqpEUw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqpEUw4.jpg&h=a4381b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上圖片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NpYIdjTlLUo&amp;t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNpYIdjTlLUo%26t&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=20501206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NpYIdjTlLUo&amp;t</a>"},{"pid":"4cc8617189edefcdd9b1be0cf7c0d131ac8e8060","tid":1975342,"uid":15799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<br />\n我睇youtube有啲滑翔機係有個摩打係機頭扯返起隻機，想了解下"},{"pid":"453dac449aff9aa34bfcc7c8499c4037c503d030","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"點知幾時要預備降落"},{"pid":"782c5e0b718b151fcc43c5803e35e87a394e2c04","tid":1975342,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"高唔高消費"},{"pid":"10956b2d407dc00ad84693ab6f82d439e5f0ee7d","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"英國係Lasham飛？"},{"pid":"7a95fb294e10fb8285767a760b82b92eb9bfffac","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453dac449aff9aa34bfcc7c8499c4037c503d030","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"點知幾時要預備降落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"所以幾時都要預備囉<br />\n<br />\n有engine 一樣要考慮engine failure 去邊到落，所以練practice forced landing 同 circuit judgement 好重要"},{"pid":"d644b7fd751645fa87de60c73ef701aa0dfa0932","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾風吹到落唔到地?"},{"pid":"222271aaa4189d36bffa97a3e557e9b28266a280","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4cc8617189edefcdd9b1be0cf7c0d131ac8e8060","tid":1975342,"uid":15799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<br />\n我睇youtube有啲滑翔機係有個摩打係機頭扯返起隻機，想了解下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪講呢種?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ug7rAfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUg7rAfd.jpg&h=49c9c366&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢款叫Powered glider，同普通glider最大分別就係多個螺旋槳(用電池/油)，咁話明係glider當然唔會長著個螺旋槳，一般都係起飛或者唔想因為唔夠高度而要迫降(我地叫out-landing)先會開幾分鐘。Powered glider又可以再分self-launching同self-sustaining兩種，分別係self-launching個馬力會足夠架glider起飛，self-sustaining就只係夠係空中維持高度或者慢慢咁爬升。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHx7M_zRUCo&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=036c09cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo</a>"},{"pid":"4818dbf811feec1d236352d993a8e0060bb1b0f0","tid":1975342,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有滑翔機牌對考cadet有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a0caa6951cf4e9aa6a41c85f397e3800d1e564","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"453dac449aff9aa34bfcc7c8499c4037c503d030","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"點知幾時要預備降落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"主要睇高度，譬如我覺得我要800ft高先可以安全咁降落。咁假設我依家飛緊4000ft高我只會大約咁樣睇下個地型睇下係咪平地，定係山區完全冇可能降落到。去到2000ft我可能就要開始諗如果依家搵唔到下一個thermal我會選擇邊塊地去降落呢，之後如果真係搵唔到下一個thermal去到1000ft我就要commit out-landing. (姐係任何情況都唔可以轉軚)。<br />\n基本上每個Cross-country glider pilot都會試過out-landing，我自己就試過係個麥田到降落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxsvhCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxsvhCS.jpg&h=79ec0dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wY1WXCV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwY1WXCV.jpg&h=549f2137&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d91cdba4587e3acff8dd40668fa1f0703c9d1f41","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"上面係麥田降落，之後點搬走？"},{"pid":"29f9945e5d94fb42c6979ba1ee9e65b1036aa69d","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"782c5e0b718b151fcc43c5803e35e87a394e2c04","tid":1975342,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"高唔高消費"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"我由零去到Sailplane Pilot License大概用左10k HKD，平過學車。英國學會平啲，因為基本上英國所有Gliding Club都唔係profit-making。由教練去到維修全部人都係義工，當我飛一轉3個鐘大概係：<br />\n起飛 Winch Launch: &pound;8-10<br />\n租架Glider: &pound;0.4 * 180 mins = &pound;72<br />\nTotal ~ &pound;80 / 3 Hrs<br />\n唔算好平但係付負擔都到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果你技術好，一般Glider租金都係cap左3-4hrs，即係你飛3個鐘同你飛6個鐘都係一樣價錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b808496fb8715af6eecbd6bd041d536900b2d54","tid":1975342,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f9945e5d94fb42c6979ba1ee9e65b1036aa69d","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"782c5e0b718b151fcc43c5803e35e87a394e2c04","tid":1975342,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"高唔高消費"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"我由零去到Sailplane Pilot License大概用左10k HKD，平過學車。英國學會平啲，因為基本上英國所有Gliding Club都唔係profit-making。由教練去到維修全部人都係義工，當我飛一轉3個鐘大概係：<br />\n起飛 Winch Launch: &pound;8-10<br />\n租架Glider: &pound;0.4 * 180 mins = &pound;72<br />\nTotal ~ &pound;80 / 3 Hrs<br />\n唔算好平但係付負擔都到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果你技術好，一般Glider租金都係cap左3-4hrs，即係你飛3個鐘同你飛6個鐘都係一樣價錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"好羨慕,窮撚無松會出國只好玩flight sim"},{"pid":"f08604596dd166d30dff4dd6671cd4b2f33d77c8","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10956b2d407dc00ad84693ab6f82d439e5f0ee7d","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"英國係Lasham飛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"巴打識啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLasham應該係全世界最大既Gliding Club，我home club唔係Lasham但我係個到飛過幾次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國成地都係Gliding Club，由Brighton到Scotland都有得飛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9a486b6e911884104b48aada2d9cfaab688e5a","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7a95fb294e10fb8285767a760b82b92eb9bfffac","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453dac449aff9aa34bfcc7c8499c4037c503d030","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"點知幾時要預備降落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"所以幾時都要預備囉<br />\n<br />\n有engine 一樣要考慮engine failure 去邊到落，所以練practice forced landing 同 circuit judgement 好重要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"講得啱，2009年係Hudson River迫降左架A320既Captain Sully都有講過飛glider既經驗點樣幫佢安全降落。有興趣可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.popularmechanics.com/flight/a6309/sully-sullenberger-glider-experience/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.popularmechanics.com%2Fflight%2Fa6309%2Fsully-sullenberger-glider-experience%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=dfb99ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.popularmechanics.com/flight/a6309/sully-sullenberger-glider-experience/</a>"},{"pid":"103d895f13b97262deb435e2c0f9e664e65239e9","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d644b7fd751645fa87de60c73ef701aa0dfa0932","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾風吹到落唔到地?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e0e929737f395e5302199d0c49efaa21f558a3","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f08604596dd166d30dff4dd6671cd4b2f33d77c8","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10956b2d407dc00ad84693ab6f82d439e5f0ee7d","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"英國係Lasham飛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"巴打識啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLasham應該係全世界最大既Gliding Club，我home club唔