-04-16T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"我幾個師博都無Lasham飛，有一位都有係Scotland 飛，但我係英國就冇飛過civilian gliding club。最近係澳洲飛返<br />\n<br />\n始終都係seasonal sport，好多人全世界追住個好天氣嚟飛。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"我幾個師博都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係</span></span></strong>Lasham飛，有一位都有係Scotland 飛，但我係英國就冇飛過civilian gliding club。最近係澳洲飛返<br />\n<br />\n始終都係seasonal sport，好多人全世界追住個好天氣嚟飛。"},{"pid":"1d0e5f5c6b8acefd97b45c062da816274fe589c8","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4818dbf811feec1d236352d993a8e0060bb1b0f0","tid":1975342,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有滑翔機牌對考cadet有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"有架，不過問到你gliding 問題時你確保自己要識答 ～<br />\n<br />\n好多人自己飛過乜都唔記得，玩完就算"},{"pid":"f606978b7793c63ee02d8d663782c4fbef19c6c9","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"222271aaa4189d36bffa97a3e557e9b28266a280","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4cc8617189edefcdd9b1be0cf7c0d131ac8e8060","tid":1975342,"uid":15799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<br />\n我睇youtube有啲滑翔機係有個摩打係機頭扯返起隻機，想了解下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪講呢種?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ug7rAfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUg7rAfd.jpg&h=49c9c366&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢款叫Powered glider，同普通glider最大分別就係多個螺旋槳(用電池/油)，咁話明係glider當然唔會長著個螺旋槳，一般都係起飛或者唔想因為唔夠高度而要迫降(我地叫out-landing)先會開幾分鐘。Powered glider又可以再分self-launching同self-sustaining兩種，分別係self-launching個馬力會足夠架glider起飛，self-sustaining就只係夠係空中維持高度或者慢慢咁爬升。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHx7M_zRUCo&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=036c09cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"有位朋友入咗架有jet engine （但其實得40磅力）做sustainer 既glider, 三球野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個運動真係平有平玩，貴有貴玩...<br />\n<br />\n英國好就好在好多club用 winch，好平就上到去。澳洲就主要都係tow，要俾架tow plane油錢，同埋新手要學towing 要多好多個flight"},{"pid":"dfa7912ca78fd2ac4e5089dcf306927c8513108f","tid":1975342,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f9945e5d94fb42c6979ba1ee9e65b1036aa69d","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"782c5e0b718b151fcc43c5803e35e87a394e2c04","tid":1975342,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"高唔高消費"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"我由零去到Sailplane Pilot License大概用左10k HKD，平過學車。英國學會平啲，因為基本上英國所有Gliding Club都唔係profit-making。由教練去到維修全部人都係義工，當我飛一轉3個鐘大概係：<br />\n起飛 Winch Launch: &pound;8-10<br />\n租架Glider: &pound;0.4 * 180 mins = &pound;72<br />\nTotal ~ &pound;80 / 3 Hrs<br />\n唔算好平但係付負擔都到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果你技術好，一般Glider租金都係cap左3-4hrs，即係你飛3個鐘同你飛6個鐘都係一樣價錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"咁都幾抵屌"},{"pid":"69cd322e7521283eaaec45f154368eb4a665b5c9","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91cdba4587e3acff8dd40668fa1f0703c9d1f41","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"上面係麥田降落，之後點搬走？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"要拆件，好鬼煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1ZJCTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/