/>\n另外如果你技術好，一般Glider租金都係cap左3-4hrs，即係你飛3個鐘同你飛6個鐘都係一樣價錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"8舊水3個鐘仲平過香港學車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3824aefd687e127be07ba8237e62ef86f37343","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4f9e4feff5a3586140ea796f1bd5c01a69621bc1","tid":1975342,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1884caef005c89451d83281ad9e944aea3329640","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4818dbf811feec1d236352d993a8e0060bb1b0f0","tid":1975342,"uid":52173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有滑翔機牌對考cadet有幫助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得點都會有少少，始終飛行原理唔會因為架飛機有冇引擎而改變，同埋一個好既glider pilot一定要對氣象有好好既認識先會知邊到搵到lift。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"覺得滑翔機好似比較危險<br />\n當準備landing 時判斷錯誤<br />\n而附近又無平坦地方咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:02:53.000Z","msg":"我搵唔返個data但冇記錯gliding既意外率同死亡率係比powered flying低。我地考牌個時其中一個項目係spot landing，大概要係target既前後50ft或更少touch down，處理得好（逆風，平地／微向上斜etc) 80-100米已經可以降落到。<br />\n不過呢個問題都解釋到點解唔係度度都可以飛glider，好似香港呢啲你根本唔會搵到地方land out。<br />\n<br />\n呢個landing其實一般但可以focus個降落距離。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CSUJKx2XKL4?t=244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCSUJKx2XKL4%3Ft%3D244&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=115e4f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CSUJKx2XKL4?t=244</a><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個就係bad landing既例子 (Ground Loop)，因為一邊翼掂到啲草先咁架機就會打白鴿轉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uZPfDERA_os?t=60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuZPfDERA_os%3Ft%3D60&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=fdd5ed7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uZPfDERA_os?t=60</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WrM6UHBFtU8?t=275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWrM6UHBFtU8%3Ft%3D275&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c2aa6b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WrM6UHBFtU8?t=275</a><br />\n後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MO4JDPy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMO4JDPy.jpg&h=4cd457eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"fd86dcc064ffc2a2fe3f5e44d1d54e52681be2d3","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b18052f172598f0b76d582aab97ffac79e27777b","tid":1975342,"uid":41610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:14:43.000Z","msg":"試下先，鐘意又afford到就去馬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你體驗過自己一個人係架glider，四圍靜到得風聲同啲雀一齊飛，你一定唔會忘記呢種感覺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2DisM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2DisM6.jpg&h=d144eace&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（呢幅自己影）"},{"pid":"a4471615be0c4417d74dbcd4cb2284ab8319d69b","tid":1975342,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"係唔係會帶個膠樽屙尿"},{"pid":"a5a91ad314acf5f7a695b0456c7d984ac298b7c2","tid":1975342,"uid":35846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1912470256fec98238303421adeaf1444d6be4c","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a91ad314acf5f7a695b0456c7d984ac298b7c2","tid":1975342,"uid":35846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"有parachute 架，in case 進入咗recover唔到嘅spin 就有機會要跳。<br />\n<br />\n都有聽過隻wing spar 斷咗要跳傘逃生"},{"pid":"7cda87a9ea8c14f69075ed779c8174b6ff160701","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a4acbc70ca96cdda54e4412650da81d756da1f","tid":1975342,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"玩呢啲計唔計飛行里數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"你想計asia miles ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你想計飛行時數，就分返開non powered 同 powered <br />\n<br />\n如果你想考gliding 牌就用gliding 鐘同launch 計。有啲gliding 嘅cross country task 要計飛幾遠，但飛行里數一般唔係考牌指標。<br />\n<br />\n考powered就用返powered 嘅鐘，同里數冇關"},{"pid":"1592f8ef865c9bdd219683a056500eb5da41f3a1","tid":1975342,"uid":195125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18052f172598f0b76d582aab97ffac79e27777b","tid":1975342,"uid":41610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"係澳洲更加應該試啦，不過唔好expect 去到一報名就有得飛。<br />\n<br />\n我諗全世界都一樣，你join club就要幫埋手推飛機，洗飛機，落田拉飛機，唔係飛完拍下patpat就走人。"},{"pid":"e8bdddbebb3b2b416a7e35a7ef257f6d0be6be55","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a91ad314acf5f7a695b0456c7d984ac298b7c2","tid":1975342,"uid":35846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T01:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"