387d5e7d51175b1516589745eee0591","tid":1975342,"uid":15799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"222271aaa4189d36bffa97a3e557e9b28266a280","tid":1975342,"uid":65222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4cc8617189edefcdd9b1be0cf7c0d131ac8e8060","tid":1975342,"uid":15799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<br />\n我睇youtube有啲滑翔機係有個摩打係機頭扯返起隻機，想了解下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪講呢種?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ug7rAfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUg7rAfd.jpg&h=49c9c366&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢款叫Powered glider，同普通glider最大分別就係多個螺旋槳(用電池/油)，咁話明係glider當然唔會長著個螺旋槳，一般都係起飛或者唔想因為唔夠高度而要迫降(我地叫out-landing)先會開幾分鐘。Powered glider又可以再分self-launching同self-sustaining兩種，分別係self-launching個馬力會足夠架glider起飛，self-sustaining就只係夠係空中維持高度或者慢慢咁爬升。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgHx7M_zRUCo&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10BZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=036c09cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gHx7M_zRUCo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"巴打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係喱隻喇"}]}